Christy Knowings https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christy_Knowings 0 Christy Lorraine Knowings (born February 25, 1980) is an American actress, comedian, musician, model, writer, and dancer who served three seasons on the Nickelodeon sketch-comedy series, All That (where she replaced Alisa Reyes in 1997 and was replaced by Giovonnie Samuels in 2002). She is from The Bronx, New York.
